staff: 中文名:行尸走肉 第五季
台湾名称:阴尸路 第五季
story: The fifth season of the AMC horror–drama television series The Walking Dead is scheduled to premiere on October 12, 2014, and consist of 16 episodes. The series is based on the series of comic books of the same name by Robert Kirkman, Tony Moore, and Charlie Adlard; it was developed for television by Frank Darabont and is executive produced by Kirkman, David Alpert, Scott M. Gimple, Greg Nicotero, Tom Luse, and Gale Anne Hurd. Gimple continued the role of showrunner after assuming the position with the fourth season.
